N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 103.7 - Service

State Regulations

Service of all documents and notices shall be made by
personal service or by deposit in first class mail in a depository maintained
by the United States Postal Service. Nonpersonal service shall be deemed
complete on mailing. Notes
